OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fwindy for most with showers, perhaps
OL,7,Fmerging to a spell of rain across the
OL,8,FPennines which may turn wintry at
OL,9,Ftimes. Driest weather later in the
OL,10,Fnight especially across eastern areas
OL,11,Fwith some clear spells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FSunshine and showers during
OL,14,FSunday, these potentially heavy. A
OL,15,Fwindy day with temperatures mostly
OL,16,Faround average, but overnight frost is
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
