OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers likely for
OL,7,FMonday, with heavy downpours by
OL,8,Fafternoon. Drier by evening. Tuesday
OL,9,Fand Wednesday cloudier with occasional
OL,10,Frain and breezy, but milder with
OL,11,Fslightly above average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
